X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Jewish Fed": "https://jewishfed.org/event/real-presents-smiley-poswolsky-on-friendship-in-the-age-of-loneliness/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:jewish_fed
X-SOURCE:Jewish Fed
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260326T190000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260326T210000
DTSTAMP:20260326T190636
CREATED:20260305T003411Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260305T003411Z
UID:10002554-1774551600-1774558800@jewishfed.org
SUMMARY:REAL presents Smiley Poswolsky on Friendship in the Age of Loneliness
DESCRIPTION:How do we create and maintain real human connection in an age of AI\, digital overwhelm\, and social fragmentation? \nWhile we are more digitally connected than ever\, many people report feeling increasingly disconnected\, finding that forming and sustaining meaningful friendships as an adult is surprisingly difficult. Join workplace belonging expert and keynote speaker Adam “Smiley” Poswolsky as he explores his recent book\, Friendship in the Age of Loneliness\, and invites us to rethink friendship as an essential pillar of a well-lived life. \nIn this inspiring and optimistic talk\, Smiley will share:\n*Practical habits and accessible ways to build meaningful connections in a fast-paced world.\n*Strategies for making new friends and deepening existing relationships beyond work and family roles.\n*How small\, purposeful acts can counter isolation and help us show up for one another more fully. \nJoin us to rediscover how to prioritize the human ties that matter most. A reception and book signing will follow the event. \nThis program is part of REAL Mental Health Initiative’s Spring Speakers Series. \nRodef Sholom’s REAL Mental Health Initiative is generously supported by the Laszlo N. Tauber Family Foundation.
URL:https://jewishfed.org/event/real-presents-smiley-poswolsky-on-friendship-in-the-age-of-loneliness/
LOCATION:Congregation Rodef Sholom\, Congregation Rodef Sholom\, San Rafael\, CA\, 94903\, United States
CATEGORIES:Community Event
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://jewishfed.org/wp-content/uploads/Smiley-1-1.png
ORGANIZER;CN="Congregation Rodef Sholom":MAILTO:office@rodefsholom.org
GEO:37.9993666;-122.5235849
X-APPLE-STRUCTURED-LOCATION;VALUE=URI;X-ADDRESS=Congregation Rodef Sholom Congregation Rodef Sholom San Rafael CA 94903 United States;X-APPLE-RADIUS=500;X-TITLE=Congregation Rodef Sholom:geo:-122.5235849,37.9993666
END:VEVENT
