DESCRIPTION:<a href="https://www.bethsholomsf.org/gala" target="_blank">Det
 ails\, Tickets and Sponsorships - click here! </a><br><br><h2>Thursday\, Ma
 rch 26<br>7:00 p.m.</h2><p>Join us for our annual fundraiser in celebration
  of the stories we carry forward — the memories\, traditions\, and moments 
 that connect us across generations. <em>L’dor V’dor</em> isn’t just about h
 onoring our history\; it’s about weaving together the diverse journeys that
  make CBS the vibrant community it is today. Whether you’ve been part of ou
 r congregation for decades or joined us recently\, this is an evening to ce
 lebrate the connections that bind us together and the joy of being part of 
 something larger than ourselves.</p><p>Dresscode: Cocktail attire </p><h3><
 a href="https://www.tribute.co/ldorvdorbethsholom/" target="_blank">Share Y
 our Story</a></h3><p>What tradition did you inherit? What CBS memory stays 
 with you? What do you hope we pass forward? What tradition did you inherit?
  What CBS memory stays with you? What do you hope we pass forward? <strong>
 <b>Tell us in 60 seconds or less.</b></strong></p><p>We’re collecting video
 s\, photos\, and written reflections from across our community for “The Sto
 ries We Carry Forward” — a tribute film premiering at the gala. Your voice 
 should be in it.</p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20260323T033505Z
LOCATION:301 14th Ave\, San Francisco\, CA 94118\, USA
SEQUENCE:2
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Annual Gala
TRANSP:OPAQUE
