X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Marin Jcc": "https://www.marinjcc.org/event/israeli-folk-dance-jan-feb/2026-04-07/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:marin_jcc
X-SOURCE:Marin Jcc
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260407T130000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260407T130000
DTSTAMP:20260326T190629
CREATED:20260108T230015Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260319T221106Z
UID:10001886-1775566800-1775566800@www.marinjcc.org
SUMMARY:Israeli Folk Dance!
DESCRIPTION:January 6-February 10 \nTuesdays from 1:00-2:45 PM \n  \n  \nDancing is great for the mind\, body\, and soul\, and it’s also fun! We’ll be dancing to a wonderful assortment of Israeli and world music. The first hour is tailored to beginners and includes learning and dancing easy-to-follow dances. The second hour moves into intermediate-level dancing and includes popular old and new dances. The class is a great way to get started\, return to\, or just keep on dancing in a friendly and supportive environment. Come for one hour or both. Newcomers welcome.\n\n  \nMembers of the OMJCC: Free\nNon-members:\n\n6-Class Pack: $50\nDrop-In: $10 per class\n\n  \nPlease register in advance to reserve your spot.
URL:https://www.marinjcc.org/event/israeli-folk-dance-jan-feb/2026-04-07/
LOCATION:Osher Marin JCC\, 200 North San Pedro Road\, San Rafael\, CA\, 94903\, United States
CATEGORIES:FItness Event,Jewish Life
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://www.marinjcc.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/New-Israeli-Dance-3.png
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Marin Jcc": "https://www.marinjcc.org/event/game-on-mexican-train-rummikub-scrabble-4/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:marin_jcc
X-SOURCE:Marin Jcc
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260407T130000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260407T150000
DTSTAMP:20260326T190629
CREATED:20260316T222829Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260316T222836Z
UID:10001868-1775566800-1775574000@www.marinjcc.org
SUMMARY:Game On! Mexican Train\, Rummikub & Scrabble
DESCRIPTION:Join others for a delightful afternoon of fun and games – literally! Choose from one of three games. Learn and play! \n\nMexican Train has become a popular game with dominos in which the goal is for participants to play all of the tiles from their hands onto one or more chains – or trains – emanating from a central hub or “station.” \n\nRummikub is a tile-based game for 2 or more players combining elements of the card game rummy and mahjong. \n\nScrabble is a popular word game for 2-4 players where participants use letter tiles to create words on a board\, aiming to connect them to existing words (similar to a crossword puzzle). \n\nPlayers of all levels are welcome! \n\nSpace is limited. Advance registration required.
URL:https://www.marinjcc.org/event/game-on-mexican-train-rummikub-scrabble-4/
LOCATION:Osher Marin JCC\, 200 North San Pedro Road\, San Rafael\, CA\, 94903\, United States
CATEGORIES:Adult Learning
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://www.marinjcc.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/https___cdn.evbuc_.com_images_1167465993_44784881969_1_original-1.jpeg
END:VEVENT
