X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Marin Jcc": "https://www.marinjcc.org/event/midweek-musical-matinee-klezmer-and-friends/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:marin_jcc
X-SOURCE:Marin Jcc
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260408T130000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260408T140000
DTSTAMP:20260326T190629
CREATED:20260316T221414Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260316T221604Z
UID:10001862-1775653200-1775656800@www.marinjcc.org
SUMMARY:Midweek Musical Matinee: "Klezmer and Friends"
DESCRIPTION:Come join us for a live\, in-person concert filled with beautiful music and interesting insights. \n\nKlezmer\, in its essence\, has always been about joy for its own sake. \nIn honor of the Passover holiday\, join accordionist Dan Cantrell\, visiting from Los Angeles\, and clarinetist Asaf Ophir\, for a delightful matinee devoted exactly to that — Klezmer and joy! \n\nThese dynamic artitsts will play some classics\, some favorites\, some oldies\, some newbies\, and some more exotic tunes that just go so well together that they couldn’t pass them up. \n\nMixed in with interesting storytelling\, this is going to be a most memorable event!
URL:https://www.marinjcc.org/event/midweek-musical-matinee-klezmer-and-friends/
LOCATION:Osher Marin JCC\, 200 North San Pedro Road\, San Rafael\, CA\, 94903\, United States
CATEGORIES:Adult Learning
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/webp:https://www.marinjcc.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/image-2.webp
END:VEVENT
