SUMMARY:MJ - Hike (10+ attending)
DESCRIPTION:Mountain Jew\n🔒 Want to attend? This Meetup won't show location or tickets — full access is in the "About Mountain Jew" section below.\n🌄 MJ Hikes — Good views\, great people\, and a rotating crew of young Jewish professionals hitting scenic trails every Sunday (\\~45 min from Mountain View). Hikes typically run 2–4 hours.\n📍 Location\nShared with verified MJ members only for security.\n🥾 What to expect\n• Social\, welcoming group\n• All levels welcome (check the specific hike details)\n• A great way to meet people and get outside\n——————————————————\n✡️ About Mountain Jew\nMountain Jew is a community exclusively for Jewish young professionals in the Bay Area. Jewish people make up less than 0.2% of the world's population\, so having spaces like this to connect with one another is incredibly meaningful — we kindly ask that this be respected.\nThis is where people don't just show up to events — they actually meet\, connect\, and build real friendships. From hikes to dinners to social gatherings\, it's a community that's active\, welcoming\, and easy to plug into.For the comfort and safety of our members\, full event details (including exact locations) are shared only with verified MJ members.\n➡️ Join us: https://mountainjew.org\nGet verified to access the full calendar\, RSVP to events\, and join the WhatsApp community.
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/mountain-jew/events/313917105/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260323T210415Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260323T210415Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/event/3/6/b/e/600_533354014.jpeg
