CREATED:20260320T185820Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260320T185820Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/event/3/1/7/8/600_533292664.jpeg
END:VEVENT
