DESCRIPTION:Start your weekend on a high note with a relaxed\, open-air gathering at the Marin Country Mart! There’s no “right way” to show up; just grab some takeout from your favorite Mart vendor and join us at the Mart for a casual community night. We’ll have a creative art project for all ages\, followed by a short\, musical Shabbat to welcome the weekend together. \nThis is a great\, low-key way for families\, neighbors\, and community members to meet new people and experience Shabbat—the Jewish tradition of taking a breath and unplugging after a long week. Everyone is welcome; bring a friend and your favorite local bites!
