UID:10002375-1776619800-1776630600@jewishfed.org
SUMMARY:JFCS East Bay Art of Living 2026
DESCRIPTION:Join us for JFCS East Bay’s Art of Living 2026\, our signature celebration of community\, resilience\, and care. Together\, we will honor the stories that shape our East Bay neighbors\, from newcomers finding safety and belonging to families and seniors building brighter futures. The evening will feature inspiring speakers\, local artists\, and opportunities to support the essential services that help thousands thrive. \nCelebrate with us as we continue the art of living with compassion\, connection\, and hope.
