SUMMARY:Israel in Focus with Jerusalem Post’s\, Herb Keinon
DESCRIPTION:Bay Area Jewish Singles Havurah\nGet the perspective beyond the headlines. Join us for a special event with the Jerusalem Post’s Herb Keinon\, as part of the Jewish Federations of North America “Israel in Focus” national tour.\n\nThrough expert analysis and timely updates\, Keinon will lead a deep dive into the Israel–Hamas conflict and the evolving challenges facing the region. This is a unique opportunity to move beyond the news cycle\, engage in meaningful dialogue\, and strengthen our collective understanding. Registration required [HERE](https://host.nxt.blackbaud.com/registration-form/?formId=d026ea05-8467-4c22-a9bb-65dcb5f8e351&envId=p-gQxjDCa1DkiFLH21jxgFhg&zone=usa)\n\nWe can go out for dinner after the event for those who are interested.
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/bay-area-jewish-singles-havurah/events/313566009/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260228T004014Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260228T004014Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/event/8/1/e/3/600_505833251.jpeg
END:VEVENT
