SUMMARY:Creating Hope: Pathways to Strength
DESCRIPTION:The annual gala celebrating the 34th anniversary of Shalom Bayit\, the Bay Area’s center for domestic violence prevention and response within the Jewish community. Includes a reception\, strolling dinner\, and speaker program. \nThis year’s event will shine a light on financial abuse and how Shalom Bayit helps survivors achieve economic independence and safety. \n  \nChaired by Sandi Bragar & Jerome Rossen
